OL,3,CStaff failed to protect residents at
OL,4,Ccare home where seven died of Covid
OL,6,FMeasures to protect residents from
OL,7,FCovid at a care home where seven
OL,8,Felderly people died were not
OL,9,F"effectively or consistently" followed
OL,10,Fby staff, a coroner has ruled.
OL,12,FWilliam Wilkinson, 102, Doris Lockett,
OL,13,F92, Roy Gilliam, 96, Jean Hartley, 81,
OL,14,FSusan Skinner, 70, Ronald Bampfylde,
OL,15,F92, and Stanislawa Koch, 93 died
OL,16,Fbetween March and April 2021 after
OL,17,Fcontracting Covid while living at
OL,18,FHolmesley Care Home, in Sidford.
