OL,3,CStaff failed to protect residents at
OL,4,Ccare home where seven died of Covid
OL,6,FThe deaths all came at the height of
OL,7,Fthe Covid pandemic when rules were in
OL,8,Fplace intended to protect residents
OL,9,Ffrom infection.
OL,11,FDuring the two-week inquest in Exeter,
OL,12,Fit was alleged that some staff refused
OL,13,Fto wear face masks or PPE, that others
OL,14,Fcontinued working despite testing
OL,15,Fpositive for the virus, and that
OL,16,Flateral flow test results were ignored.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/16
