OL,3,CStaff failed to protect residents at
OL,4,Ccare home where seven died of Covid
OL,6,FOn Thursday 17 October, coroner for
OL,7,FDevon, Plymouth and Torbay Alison
OL,8,FLonghorn concluded that there were
OL,9,Fproper processes at the home but they
OL,10,F"were not effectively or consistently
OL,11,Ffollowed" by all of its staff.
OL,13,FA family member of one of the
OL,14,Fresidents placed seven red roses on a
OL,15,Fdesk in the court to represent the
OL,16,Fresidents who died.
OL,18,FA spokesperson for Holmesley Care Home
OL,19,Fsaid it acknowledged the coroner's
OL,20,Ffindings and has made improvements to
OL,21,Fcare provision in the home.
OL,26,@rD@AOUsD@IO]
