OL,3,CStaff failed to protect residents at
OL,4,Ccare home where seven died of Covid
OL,6,FThe inquest was told two staff members
OL,7,F- manager Joanne Burchell and night-
OL,8,Ftime nurse Christos Provistallis - had
OL,9,Fbeen arrested on suspicion of ill-
OL,10,Ftreatment or wilful neglect, but no
OL,11,Ffurther action was taken against them.
OL,13,FIt heard allegations that Mr
OL,14,FProvistallis had ignored guidance to
OL,15,Fwear a face mask and told people he
OL,16,Fbelieved Covid-19 was a conspiracy.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/16
