OL,3,CStaff failed to protect residents at
OL,4,Ccare home where seven died of Covid
OL,6,FDeputy manager Jemma Turner told the
OL,7,Finquest about being telephoned by a
OL,8,Fcare worker in the early hours of 2
OL,9,FMarch reporting several residents were
OL,10,Fill.
OL,12,F"She was crying, saying, 'Jemma, the
OL,13,Fresidents are poorly, I don't know
OL,14,Fwhat to do'," Mrs Turner said.
OL,16,F"I said, 'Where's the nurse?' and she
OL,17,Fsaid, 'He's refusing to wear a mask
OL,18,Fand he's walking around the home and
OL,19,Fhe's saying that Covid is a
OL,20,Fconspiracy'."
