OL,3,CStaff failed to protect residents at
OL,4,Ccare home where seven died of Covid
OL,6,FOthers alleged Mrs Burchell decided
OL,7,Fagainst sending sick staff home due to
OL,8,Fstaff shortages and had ignored
OL,9,Fpositive lateral flow test results
OL,10,Fputting them down to a "bad batch".
OL,12,FThe inquest heard from the home's
OL,13,Fowner, Will Neal, who told the inquest
OL,14,Fhe "felt uneasy" about Mrs Burchell's
OL,15,Fdecisions, but said she made them "in
OL,16,Fthe best interests and overall safety
OL,17,Fof the residents".
OL,19,FHe also told the hearing he regretted
OL,20,Fnot dismissing the nurse who had
OL,21,Frefused to wear a face mask.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/16
