OL,3,CStaff failed to protect residents at
OL,4,Ccare home where seven died of Covid
OL,6,F"I feel really upset and I feel really
OL,7,Fdisappointed," he said. "The situation
OL,8,Fof not wearing a mask, when he should
OL,9,Fhave been wearing a mask
OL,10,Fappropriately, is really, really
OL,11,Fdisappointing to hear."
OL,13,FThe inquest heard staff had realised
OL,14,Fthere was potentially an outbreak on
OL,15,Fthe morning of 2 March, but days
OL,16,Fbefore six positive results had been
OL,17,Fignored.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/16
