OL,4,Ccare home where seven died of Covid
OL,6,FThree days later on 5 March, Mrs
OL,7,FTurner contacted health watchdog the
OL,8,FCare Quality Commission (CQC), Devon
OL,9,Fsafeguarding and the police with her
OL,10,Fconcerns about the outbreak.
OL,12,FMr Neal said he did not know any of
OL,13,Fthis until he was told days later by
OL,14,FMrs Turner in a whistleblowing email.
OL,16,F"When I did hear about that I thought
OL,17,Fthat was unthinkable," he said. "The
OL,18,Fidea that six people would be
OL,19,Fcoughing, displaying symptoms of Covid-
OL,20,F19, and tested positive, and we just
OL,21,Fignored it and called the GP."
