OL,3,CStaff failed to protect residents at
OL,4,Ccare home where seven died of Covid
OL,6,FAfter hearing that two people had been
OL,7,Farrested and interviewed by police
OL,8,Ffollowing the Covid-19 outbreak, the
OL,9,Frelatives of those who died criticised
OL,10,Fthe decision not to prosecute anyone.
OL,12,FWladek Kock, whose mother Stanislawa
OL,13,FKoch died, told the inquest the
OL,14,Fauthorities did not have the "courage"
OL,15,Fto prosecute.
OL,17,FSally Burns, the daughter of Mr
OL,18,FBampflyde, added she was "absolutely
OL,19,Fastounded" by how events unfolded.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/16
