OL,4,Ccare home where seven died of Covid
OL,6,FRecording her conclusions, Ms Longhorn
OL,7,Fsaid: "Whilst the nursing home had
OL,8,Fclear policies and processes to be
OL,9,Ffollowed to reduce the risk of
OL,10,Finfection and spread of Covid-19,
OL,11,Fthese were not effectively or
OL,12,Fconsistently followed by all staff
OL,13,Fworking in the home."
OL,26,@oD@GOUuD@UO]
