OL,3,CStaff failed to protect residents at
OL,4,Ccare home where seven died of Covid
OL,6,FShe added: "We have heard much
OL,7,Fevidence that some staff at Holmesley
OL,8,Fdid not effectively or consistently
OL,9,Ffollow clearly defined processes
OL,10,Fregarding infection prevention and
OL,11,Fcontrol and that their practice of not
OL,12,Fdoing so potentially put that home at
OL,13,Frisk of infection.
OL,15,F"I would highlight that evidence heard
OL,16,Fat this inquest related to only some
OL,17,Fstaff at one care home.
OL,26,@nD@LOUwD@AOU
