OL,3,CStaff failed to protect residents at
OL,4,Ccare home where seven died of Covid
OL,6,F"I would like to thank all the
OL,7,Ffamilies of the residents, I recognise
OL,8,Fthat some of the evidence may have
OL,9,Fbeen upsetting or difficult to hear
OL,10,Fand I understand their frustration
OL,11,Fthat no criminal prosecution will be
OL,12,Fbrought.
OL,14,F"I want to offer all of you affected
OL,15,Fby the loss of your loved ones my
OL,16,Fcondolences, I really am very sorry
OL,17,Ffor your losses."
OL,19,FThe coroner also acknowledged recent
OL,20,FCQC reports which indicated there had
OL,21,Fbeen improvements at the home.
