OL,6,FSpeaking after the conclusion of the
OL,7,Finquest, Mick Koch, whose mother
OL,8,FStanislawa Koch died after contracting
OL,9,Fthe virus, said he "still feels there
OL,10,Fhasn't been justice in the situation".
OL,12,F"We can see a small, creeping forward
OL,13,Fin improving situations in this sort
OL,14,Fof event, so the mismanagement of the
OL,15,FCovid outbreak at Holmesley can't
OL,16,Fhappen again.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/16
