OL,6,FA spokesperson for Holmesley Nursing
OL,7,FHome, said: "We have at all times co-
OL,8,Foperated openly, fully, and with
OL,9,Fcomplete transparency with these
OL,10,Finvestigations and are grateful to
OL,11,Fnote that the coroner recognised we
OL,12,Fhad clear policies and procedures in
OL,13,Fplace to deal with the pandemic.
OL,15,F"However, we also acknowledge the
OL,16,Fcoroner's findings that these
OL,17,Fmandatory policies and procedures were
OL,18,Fnot always followed as consistently
OL,19,Fand effectively by some staff members
OL,20,Fas they ought to have been.
